reviews.text: A big spacious restaurant.  The restaurant have many big tables and can serve huge amount of customers.  I came here with a group of 16 people and we were able to sit closely.  The food is decent although the price is quite high than typical restaurant of the same type.  However the BBQ food is very good.

Dinner is not tasty at all for the 6 dishes that we ordered.

I passed by and having a hot porridge for breakfast this morning.  It's not bad, with a dish of rice paste rolls 腸粉。  this is better than my dinner last night
comfortable place, price slightly high.
Excellent selection of food n great service attitude by the servers.  They don't rush you out.
Hong Kong taste

reviews.text: 燒味👍👍👍
炒嘢食 火鴨絲炆米 等咗45分鐘離譜28.7.2019
價錢可比得上酒樓,欵式多選擇,唯出品不及酒樓,不值這個價錢！
燒味不錯，小炒也味道很好，午市中式套餐很快沽清。

不愧係一代名店，七十年代廣播道外賈專家，不少名星藝員也嘗過知味! 現在也有50~60%
水準保留!
